    "_nat1_note": "With [lethal] tag, a natural 1 = instant death. Otherwise nat 1 is a critical failure."
  },
  "combat": {
    "_note": "Opposed rolls: attacker (die+mod)*power vs defender (die+mod)*power. Attacker wins -> damage scaled by margin ratio.",
